description: Today I will be teaching you the basics of cupcake decorating. This includes making fondant decorations, colouring buttercream and piping your icing. I will bake the cupcakes beforehand so they are ready to decorate when you arrive and each person will get to take their decorated cupcakes home with them. Please bring a tupperware box with you for your cupcakes. There will be 6 cupcakes per person and I ask a fee of 10 euros per person to cover my costs. The class will be taught all in English.
how_to_find_us: Location will be emailed to attendees
name: The Basics of Cupcake Decorating

description:
Today we will make cupcakes with my favourite theme... Pigs! I will show you how to make fondant pigs swimming in little cupcake mud baths and full face pig cupcakes.
I will bake the cupcakes beforehand so they are ready to decorate when you arrive. Each person will have 6 cupcakes to decorate and take home. Please bring your own tupperware box to take your cupcakes home. The price for this workshop is €10 and will be in English.
name: Piggy Cupcakes

description:
Today we will turn our cupcakes into mini cheeseburgers! I will show you how to build your burgers, make salad and cheese from fondant icing and shredded coconut and we will even make cones of French fries from fondant! 

I will bake the cupcakes beforehand so they are ready for decorating when you arrive. Each person will make 6 burger cupcakes, please bring a Tupperware box with you to transport your cupcakes home. The price for this workshop is €12 and it will be taught in English.
name: Mini cheeseburger cupcakes

description:
Today we will be making garden themed cupcakes. I will be teaching you how to make different bugs, butterflies and flowers from fondant and I will show you how to pipe icing to look like grass.

The cupcakes will be baked beforehand so that they are ready to decorate when you arrive. Each person will have 6 cupcakes to decorate, please bring a large Tupperware box with you to transport your cupcakes back home.

For anyone who has not attended a workshop before, I ask for a €5 deposit to be paid into my bank account before the class. This is to cover my costs if people don't turn up on the day, as I will have already paid for the ingredients and baked the cupcakes.
name: In The Garden Cupcakes
